name: plaster_pastedeploy
raw_meta_yaml:
{% set name = "plaster_pastedeploy" %}
{% set version = "0.7" %}

package:
  name: "{{ name|lower }}"
  version: "{{ version }}"

source:
  url: https://pypi.io/packages/source/{{ name[0] }}/{{ name }}/{{ name }}-{{ version }}.tar.gz
  sha256: 391d93a4e1ff81fc3bae27508ebb765b61f1724ae6169f83577f06b6357be7fd

build:
  noarch: python
  number: 0
  script: "{{ PYTHON }} -m pip install . -vv"

requirements:
  host:
    - pip
    - python
    - setuptools
  run:
    - pastedeploy >=1.5.0
    - plaster >=0.5
    - python

test:
  imports:
    - plaster_pastedeploy

about:
  home: https://github.com/Pylons/plaster_pastedeploy
  license: MIT
  license_family: MIT
  license_file: LICENSE.txt
  summary: A loader implementing the PasteDeploy syntax to be used by plaster.
  dev_url: https://github.com/Pylons/plaster_pastedeploy

extra:
  recipe-maintainers:
    - lincrosenbach
    - kfasolin
